-## 9. Common Issues
-| Symptom | Cause | Fix |
-|---------|-------|-----|
-| Locale not listed | Missing pack | Reinstall via UI or CLI |
-| Garbled characters | DB collation wrong | Ensure utf8mb4 on all tables |
-| Partial translation | Incomplete upstream locale | Contribute updates to PKP | 
+## 8. Тестване
